channel.title: Help please
channel.description: hey guys iv done everything on my server compiler works run.bat iv just opened my ports using utorrent and checked canyouseeme.org and its all good but when i run my server i run no-ip program and when i try login using the ip-changer client etc it says "unexpected server response please login using a different world" and in my runserver console its saying connection received from my ip etc i just cant log in :S? any help?

item.title: Help please
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

The server will be rejecting the incoming connection, make sure the client and server are compatible with each other (example: a 317 client and a 317 server would connect, a 508 client and a 317 server wouldn’t). Another possible cause of this error can be that your IP address is blacklisted from connecting, check configuration files.
